&q;,&q;value&q;:&q;&l;p&g;The following complementary information is available:&l;/p&g;&l;ul&g;  &l;li&g;Read the &l;a href=\&q;https://www.fao.org/3/cd7067en/online/cd7067en.html\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q; class=\&q;external-link-new-window\&q; title=\&q;Opens external link in new window\&q;&g;&l;em&g;full digital report&l;/em&g;&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;Read the &l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7071en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;&l;em&g;In Brief&l;/em&g;&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;Read the &l;em&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7233en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;Policy brief: Tackling land degradation for sustainable agrifood systems&l;/a&g;&l;/em&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;Read the &l;em&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7161en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;Policy brief: Global crop production patterns across landholding scales to inform policies&l;/a&g;&l;/em&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g; Read the &l;em&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://www.fao.org/interactive/2025/tackling-land-degradation/en/\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;Interactive story: Addressing Land Degradationfor a Sustainable Future&l;/a&g;&l;/em&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g; Watch the video: &l;a href=\&q;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MOJGEn_HC8I\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;&l;em&g;The State of Food and Agriculture 2025&l;/em&g;&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;Read the press release: &l;a href=\&q;https://www.fao.org/newsroom/detail/fao-report--1.7-billion-people-experience-lower-crop-yields-due-to-land-degradation/en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;&l;em&g;FAO report: 1.7 billion people experience lower crop yields due to land degradation&l;/em&g;&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;Read &l;em&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd2616en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;The State of Food and Agriculture 2024&l;/a&g;&l;/em&g;&l;/li&g;&l;/ul&g;&l;p&g;Read the background papers:&l;/p&g;&l;ul&g;  &l;li&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7067en-supplementarydata\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;SOFA 2025 supplementary data&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7317en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;A global yield gap assessment to link land degradation to socioeconomic risks&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7324en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;Policies that improved land conditions&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7217en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;Revealing complementarities across farm scales in global food production&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;  &l;li&g;&l;a href=\&q;https://doi.org/10.4060/cd7373en\&q; target=\&q;_blank\&q;&g;A global update on the number of farms, farm size and farmland distribution&l;/a&g;&l;/li&g;&l;/ul&g;&l;p&g;Updated 02/02/2026&l;/p&g;&l;p&g;&l;strong&g;Previous version&l;/strong&g;&l;/p&g;&l;p&g;Views = 18,202 | Downloads = 17,491&l;/p&g;&q;,&q;place&q;:0,&q;authority&q;:null,&q;confidence&q;:-1}],&q;fao.sdgs&q;:[{&q;uuid&q;:&q;9f032033-1dd2-4f7e-b2ac-38a51c85bc82&q;,&q;language&q;:&q;&q;,&q;value&q;:&q;15. Protect, restore and promote sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems, sustainably manage forests, combat desertification, and halt and reverse land degradation and halt biodiversity loss&q;,&q;place&q;:0,&q;authority&q;:null,&q;confidence&q;:-1}],&q;fao.specialapprover.identifier&q;:[{&q;uuid&q;:&q;95c1fe91-d5ed-4220-8a9b-e5f51237266c&q;,&q;language&q;:&q;&q;,&q;value&q;:&q;17&q;,&q;place&q;:0,&q;authority&q;:null,&q;confidence&q;:-1}],&q;fao.subject.agrovoc&q;:[{&q;uuid&q;:&q;5c1a1f9c-ab89-4aa2-9f5c-02b4dc70a9ff&q;,&q;language&q;:&q;en&q;,&q;value&q;:&q;farmland&q;,&q;place&q;:0,&q;authority&q;:&q;ba978de8e9e6b218545595d083371ce4da870577&q;,&q;confidence&q;:600},{&q;uuid&q;:&q;66845c07-f6d1-4c2a-8207-e7a1f65793e8&q;,&q;language&q;:&q;en&q;,&q;value&q;:&q;land use&q;,&q;place&q;:1,&q;authority&q;:&q;e7489f64128f2e2c0d2aa74ab617d8aadacd7dbe&q;,&q;confidence&q;:600},{&q;uuid&q;:&q;767c09c1-ec3c-4fc4-ac3e-7e9b78bd0ae4&q;,&q;language&q;:&q;en&q;,&q;value&q;:&q;land degradation&q;,&q;place&q